<title>CROATIA: Croatian hotelier Makarska to auction two hotels.</title>
<headline>Croatian hotelier Makarska to auction two hotels.</headline>
<dateline>ZAGREB 1997-06-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Croatian southern Adriatic hotelier Hoteli Makarska on Friday advertised a public auction for two of its hotels on July 5.</p>
<p>In an advertisement in daily Slobodna Dalmacija it gave the starting price for each of the two three-star facilities -- Miramare and Osejava -- as 1.8 million German marks.</p>
<p>The auction will be held at Hotel Meteor in Makarska. All Croatian and foreign interested parties are invited to submit their bids by July 1.</p>
<p>-- Zagreb Newsroom, 385-1-4557075</p>
